現實確實亦唔係咁，公開試成績只係for 你入大學，或者係第一份工，之後都係睇你大學學位and/or 工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n呢個亦反證，根本唔洗咁執著面對公開試既階段時，係咪應該只有公開試定要有埋其他野<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔係好明我講乜，咁當我無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e73451be9099186262f678977d57e590a1ee66","tid":1186397,"uid":74462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24ba662180dfd03f99eeb101952f3aac6cc95d3d","tid":1186397,"uid":53278,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:40:58.000Z","msg":"計其他野 班窮撚仲邊有書讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD課外活動你估平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef4bb26df64d4fb5341653418c621c3107710bd","tid":1186397,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:44:07.000Z","msg":"唔淨睇公開試既話，睇埋課外活動？比賽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁咪仲唔公平，你家境成為決定因素。"}]}